---
message_id: "{{ msg.message_id | replace('"', '\\"') }}"
thread_id: "{{ msg.thread_id or '' }}"
title: "{{ msg.subject | replace('"', '\\"') }}"
type: mail-message
source: "{{ msg.source or 'mail' }}"
sender: "[[contacts/{{ msg.sender_email }}]]"
sender_name: "{{ (msg.sender_name or '') | replace('"', '\\"') }}"
from: "{{ msg.sender_email }}"
date: {{ msg.date.strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S%z') }}
mailbox: "{{ msg.mailbox or '' }}"
has_attachments: {{ msg.has_attachments | lower }}
{% if msg.recipients %}
recipients:
{% for addr in msg.recipients %}  - "{{ addr | replace('"', '\\"') }}"
{% endfor %}{% endif %}
{% if msg.cc %}
cc:
{% for addr in msg.cc %}  - "{{ addr | replace('"', '\\"') }}"
{% endfor %}{% endif %}
{% if msg.attachments %}
attachments:
{% for name in msg.attachments %}  - "{{ name | replace('"', '\\"') }}"
{% endfor %}{% endif %}
tags: [почта]
created: {{ now }}
---

# {{ msg.subject }}

| Поле | Значение |
|------|----------|
| 📨 От | {% if msg.sender_name %}{{ msg.sender_name }} <{{ msg.sender_email }}>{% else %}{{ msg.sender_email }}{% endif %} |
| 📅 Дата | {{ msg.date.strftime('%d.%m.%Y %H:%M') }} |
| 📁 Ящик | {{ msg.mailbox or "—" }} |
{% if msg.recipients %}| 📬 Кому | {{ msg.recipients | join(", ") }} |
{% endif %}{% if msg.cc %}| 👥 Копия | {{ msg.cc | join(", ") }} |
{% endif %}
{% if msg.attachments %}
## Вложения

{% for name in msg.attachments %}
- 📎 {{ name }}
{% endfor %}
{% elif msg.has_attachments %}
## Вложения

_Имена вложений недоступны — включите PA\_MAIL\_FETCH\_BODY=true для их получения._
{% endif %}

{% if msg.body %}
## Текст письма

{{ msg.body }}
{% endif %}
